          "tz": 0
        },
        "subject": "LU-12040 lod: fix defect in lod_verify_v1v3",
        "message": "LU-12040 lod: fix defect in lod_verify_v1v3\n\nIn case of replay lum->lmm_stripe_offset does not contain stripe\noffset but layout generation. Taking it as ost index causes\nlod_check_index_in_pool to return EINVAL and the replay to fail.\n\nTake ost indexes from lum3->lmm_objects and check for their\npresence in pool.\n\nSigned-off-by: Vladimir Saveliev <c17830@cray.com>\nChange-Id: I875c9e51826e827a78d0cd1f5c30160d982a3728\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
